OL,3,CAirport to get 'major redesign' with
OL,4,Cnew restaurant and runway views
OL,6,FTravellers can expect a new
OL,7,Frestaurant, an updated retail space,
OL,8,Fquiet zones, and views over the runway
OL,9,Fas part of a "major redesign" of the
OL,10,FJersey Airport departures area.
OL,12,FWork will start in August and is
OL,13,Fexpected to last around 14 months,
OL,14,Fwith Ports of Jersey admitting there
OL,15,Fwill be some disruption as the new
OL,16,Fvision takes shape.
