OL,3,CAirport to get 'major redesign' with
OL,4,Cnew restaurant and runway views
OL,6,FHowever, officials promise to bring a
OL,7,F"fresher, more welcoming experience to
OL,8,Fpassengers - all with a big nod to the
OL,9,Fisland's unique character, natural
OL,10,Fbeauty, and vibrant culture".
OL,12,FThe previous free-to-use upstairs
OL,13,Fviewing area of the runway has already
OL,14,Fbeen converted into a paid lounge,
OL,15,Fwhich will welcome its first guests
OL,16,Fthis week.
