OL,3,CAirport to get 'major redesign' with
OL,4,Cnew restaurant and runway views
OL,6,FPorts of Jersey says costs and
OL,7,Fdetailed designs are still being
OL,8,Fworked on, but it wants to better
OL,9,Fserve the needs of travellers that
OL,10,Fhave changed since the departure area
OL,11,Ffirst opened in 1997.
OL,13,FIt adds that the investment will be
OL,14,Fcentred around comfort and
OL,15,Faccessibility, whilst aiming to give
OL,16,Fpassengers a "memorable last
OL,17,Fimpression of Jersey".
OL,19,FWhat is included in the departure
OL,20,Flounge redevelopment?
