OL,3,CAirport to get 'major redesign' with
OL,4,Cnew restaurant and runway views
OL,6,FThe project follows public feedback
OL,7,Fthat Ports says showed a desire for
OL,8,Fauthentic local touches over generic
OL,9,Ftravel spaces.
OL,11,FThe first phase of works will see back-
OL,12,Foffice areas cleared to create
OL,13,Ftemporary walkways for when the main
OL,14,Fconstruction begins.
OL,16,FSeating areas will also be moved, a
OL,17,Fpop-up cafe will be set up and the
OL,18,Fairport's disruption desk will be
OL,19,Fremoved.
