OL,3,CAirport to get 'major redesign' with
OL,4,Cnew restaurant and runway views
OL,6,FMatt Thomas, Chief Executive Officer
OL,7,Fof Ports of Jersey, says: "As with any
OL,8,Fproject of this scale, there will be
OL,9,Fsome disruption as we build a much
OL,10,Fmore welcoming, efficient, and
OL,11,Funmistakably Jersey space for
OL,12,Ftravellers.
OL,14,F"We really appreciate everyone's
OL,15,Fpatience and look forward to
OL,16,Fdelivering something the whole island
OL,17,Fcan feel proud of."
